Welcome to project fnatic, a professional and player-based server hosted off a 24/7 vps. Project fnatic was founded 3 years ago only it was called "fnaticscape". Back then i was just messing around now it's for real. This is mostly a fun server with easy access to pking and plenty more, if your wondering where the name "fnatic" comes from it is from the term "fanatic" meaning "a person whose enthusiasm or zeal for something is extreme or beyond normal limits" or "a person devoted to a particular hobby or pastime"
